This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning, which are both covered by the Computer Science sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves the use of unsupervised learning, which falls under the sub-category cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with medical reports and classification, which could fall under the sub-categories cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves the use of textual data, which could also fall under the sub-category cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
